RUGBY UNION - FRANCE BEAT ROMANIA 51 - 20 . France beat Romania 51 - 20 ( halftime 29 - 10 ) in their rugby union test on Sunday . Scorers : Romania - Tries : Romeo Gontineac , Margarit Radoi . Penalties : Neculai Nichitean ( 2 ) . Conversions : Nichitean ( 2 ) . France - Tries : David Venditti ( 2 ) , Philippe Bernat - Salles ( 2 ) , Olivier Viars ( 2 ) , Abdelatif Benazzi , Alain Penaud , Olivier Merle . Conversions : Christophe Lamaison ( 2 ) , Sebastien Viars . Referee : Claudio Giacomel ( Italy ) Attendance : 10 , 000 . 
